CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 5, 1960, pg. A2, reads: "Top Union Official - Charles Larry (center), shown with Frank Blythe, left, and Ellis Hockenberry, president and secretary, respectively, of IUE Local 746, Columbus, Ohio, recently was chosen executive vice president of the 40,000 member Columbus-Franklin County AFL-CIO. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Columbus, Ohio AFL - CIO members Frank Blythe, Charles Larry, and Ellis Hockenberry, standing in interior
